M|FRON|tx|> Load this file before building any new cp or page.
M|FRON|tx|---
M|Serv|tx|\| Situation \| Directive \| Reason \|
M|Serv|tx|\|-----------\|-----------\|--------\|
M|Serv|tx|\| Displaying data fetched on server \| None (Server cp) \| No hydration cost \|
M|Serv|tx|\| Using `useState`, `useEffect`, event handlers \| `'use client'` \| Browser APIs required \|
M|Serv|tx|\| Consuming SSE stream \| `'use client'` \| `EventSource` / streaming fetch \|
M|Serv|tx|\| Reading from a cookie (vt switcher) \| None (Server cp) \| Cookies readable in RSC \|
M|Serv|tx|> `'use client'` boundary shd be placed at the lowest level that needs it. Never mark a page wrapper as client just bc a child cp needs it.
