M|Stat|tx|\| State tp \| Where to store \| Why \|
M|Stat|tx|\|-----------\|---------------\|-----\|
M|Stat|tx|\| Server data (sl stats, ag list) \| Fetch in Server cp or via `useEffect` + local state \| Simple, no global store needed \|
M|Stat|tx|\| UI state (active tab, modal open) \| `useState` in cp \| Ephemeral, not worth persisting \|
M|Stat|tx|\| Active vt \| Cookie `yvon_active_venture` \| Survives navigation, accessible server-side \|
M|Stat|tx|\| Conversation messages \| sb via ap rt \| Must persist across sn \|
M|Stat|tx|\| us preferences \| `localStorage` \| Ephemeral, device-local only \|
M|Stat|tx|No Zustand, Redux, or Jotai — this app is simple enough for local state + server data.
